WEBVTT

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:03.720
These days, schools keep
the internet away from children,

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:07.056
they pretend like it doesn’t exist.

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:09.056
What should happen is the opposite.

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:11.096
Internet should be in the school.

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:15.056
Internet should be
in the examination hall.

00:04:15.240 --> 00:04:17.800
People asked, “So you want
the children to cheat?”

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:20.285
I replied, "This is not cheating.


00:04:20.285 --> 00:04:23.716
When one has a problem in life,
doesn’t one turn to the net for answers?

00:04:23.716 --> 00:04:25.360
So why not in the exams?"

00:04:27.508 --> 00:04:32.938
(Applause)